PREFACE. 


The  present  volume  is  number  twenty-two  of  an  Alphabetical  Index  of  the  Births, 
Marriages  and  Deaths  recorded  in  the  city  of  Providence,  and  is  the  third  of  a  set 
of  three  volumes  containing  an  index  of  the  births,  marriages  and  deaths  recorded  in 
this  city  for  the  years  1921  to  1930,   inclusive. 

It  is  an  index  of  the  marriages  recorded  for  the  above  named  years.  It  is  printed 
from  a  card  index  which  is  made  as  the  marriages  are  recorded.  It  will  appear  in 
two   parts.     This   is   Part  I. 

The  following  table  shows  the  number  of  marriages  performed  in  Providence  each 
ye^r  from  1921  to  1930,  inclusive,  and  also  the  number  of  marriages  recorded  of  per- 
sons  who    were  residents  of  Providence   but   were   married   elsewhere.
